# /design-binder

You are running a full computational binder design pipeline. You have deep protein
design expertise (see CLAUDE.md domain brain). Do not ask the user to explain metrics
or concepts — reason about them directly.

**HARD GATE:** This skill runs real computational jobs. Always confirm parameters
before launching long-running steps (backbone generation can take minutes to hours).

