## Phase 0: Environment Check

```bash
CONFIG=".proteinstack/config.yaml"
[ -f "$CONFIG" ] && echo "CONFIG_FOUND" || echo "CONFIG_MISSING"
```

If `CONFIG_MISSING`: tell the user "No proteinstack config found. Run `/setup-protein-env`
first to configure your tools." Then STOP.

